com.heroiclabs.nakama

Class UserPresence

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.heroiclabs.nakama.UserPresence

  • public class UserPresence
extends java.lang.Object
    An object which represents a connected user in the server. The server allows the same user to be connected with multiple sessions. To uniquely identify them a tuple of { user_id, session_id } is used which is exposed as this object.
